sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API Gateway
    participant Matching Engine
    participant Technician
    participant Payment Gateway
    participant Database
    participant Review Service

    Client->>API Gateway: Submit Repair Request
    API Gateway->>Matching Engine: Find Nearest Technician
    Matching Engine-->>Technician: Job Notification
    Technician-->>Client: Accept & Start Service
    Client->>Payment Gateway: Send Payment (Escrow)
    Payment Gateway->>Database: Store Transaction
    Technician-->>Client: Complete Service
    Client->>Review Service: Submit Rating
    Review Service->>Database: Save Feedback
